{"tid":369254,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【心繫紅魔】朗尼：他們會享受我這入球","createTime":"2017-08-22T07:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T11:11:51.000Z","uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be0333ca3495a59c2454ad3e24f4e55f2ce3c8f1","tid":369254,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/154514_56abe4c39a1bd8285e1d6fe943033c6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F154514_56abe4c39a1bd8285e1d6fe943033c6c.jpg&h=adc16e44&s={SIZE}\" />收皮吧哥狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/154538_4895a93269e4a3ae0eaab6c09a923164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F154538_4895a93269e4a3ae0eaab6c09a923164.jpg&h=62816ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愛華頓作客1比1逼平曼城，朗尼攻入了個人第200個英超入球，賽後他表示，自己的老東家曼聯會很享受自己的這粒入球。<br />\n　　<br />\n朗尼在今年夏天離開曼聯加盟愛華頓，這次對陣曼城，朗尼用表現幫助了紅魔。「這是一個甜蜜的時刻，」朗尼賽後說，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我確信，曼徹斯特的紅色一邊也會享受這個入球的</span>。」<br />\n　　<br />\n「在比賽之前，如果說能拿一分，那挺不錯的，但賽後我們（對和波）有點遺憾。我們感覺本可以堅持到最後，也許再攻入一球，但必須稱讚曼城，他們改變了陣型，創造出了一些好機會，讓我們感到艱難。」<br />\n　　<br />\n朗尼在賽後繼續表露著對曼聯的感情，他發了一張圖片，是自己面對曼城球迷在慶祝，做出傾聽的手勢，並寫道：「<span style=\"color: red;\">看到這樣一些熟悉的面孔真是好事</span>」，顯然，這是在回應曼城球迷對他的噓聲。<br />\n　　<br />\n英格蘭教練修夫基在看台觀戰，當被問到是否想過重返英格蘭隊時，朗尼說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們看看吧，現在我專注於愛華頓。未來幾天我會和修夫基談談，會談的，看看會發生什麼</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朗隊<br />\n反西死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0358cee13420fe8ca0fde8901b26bc9be75750","tid":369254,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3313746a35d5cd5d4372dc85193aa3e427820dd3","tid":369254,"uid":49611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df16501e2ac29ccbeee0c83f77ec3589f583aa3c","tid":369254,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"月巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14525795f58962915f3a0fc4f8c8e7208e17912c","tid":369254,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"manchester is fat"},{"pid":"48c82374e3bae6e03ed814020faeb68887f50370","tid":369254,"uid":7330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"朗隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bece7ae7006947cc77d08f126b8648742925cd5","tid":369254,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"放過英格蘭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cfbfb009978e42a19687ad88fa11b563f996dd","tid":369254,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff3613ab23df95fcbbe6ecf2c9c5fc3c53bc9a6","tid":369254,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"反西註定失敗"},{"pid":"4d0d2da53c932a8d1b0bdac742807d7af64cdaf9","tid":369254,"uid":38938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"反西又輸"}]}